cards.title: Emraan Hashmi on Aryan Khan Intimacy Coaches and His Musical Legacy With Yami Gautam
cards.abstract: New Delhi, Nov. 10 -- Yami Gautam and Emraan Hashmi share exclusive behind-the-scenes stories from their upcoming film Haq, revealing never-heard-before moments and emotional insights. Watch this Bollywood Ke Kisse interview for candid revelations, fun banter, and deep conversations about acting, justice, and cinema. Bollywood Ke Kisse brings you an exclusive and unfiltered conversation with Yami Gautam and Emraan Hashmi ahead of their highly awaited film Haq. In this fun yet powerful interview, Niki dives deep into the emotional core of the film, the real-life landmark judgment that inspired it, and how the actors approached their most intense roles yet. From Yami's honest breakdown of her preparation to Emraan's transformation into a never-seen-before avatar, this interview blends storytelling, nostalgia, laughter, and meaningful conversations - the perfect Bollywood Ke Kisse cocktail.
